<%= stylesheet_link_tag "main" %>
<h1>Welcome to IndieSpot</h1>
<p>This is an independent music library that catalogs some of the best bands that haven't seen the limelight</p>

<% if session[:user_id] == nil%>
    <p>Three years old, but still fresh in our minds.</p>
    <p>Joyce Manor - Never Hungover Again</p>
    <%= image_tag 'Never Hungover Again.png' %>
    <p>Want to check out this and more? Create an account!</p>

    <p>Create New User</P>
    <%= form_tag :action => 'index' do %>
        Username:  <%= text_field_tag 'username', @myUser %> <br>
        Email:     <%= email_field_tag 'email', 'email@example.com'%><br>
        Password:  <%= password_field_tag 'password', nil, maxlength: 12 %><br>
        <%= submit_tag 'Create' %>
    <% end %>

<% else %>
    <p> Thanks for coming by IndieSpot!  All feedback or input is welcome!</p>

    <p>In recent news, Grizzly Bear has released a new Single of their upcoming album Painted Ruins!</p>
    <p>Click the album art to listen on Youtube.</p>
    <p>Expect Painted Ruins on IndieSpot on August 18th!</p>
    <%= link_to image_tag('Three Rings - Single.png'), "https://youtu.be/PZ8LB6KHHMs" %>

<% end %>